本劇原先為許多待製作的節目之一，由於主創[[查克·洛里|查克·洛里]]在2012年9月與華納兄弟簽下為期四年的新合約，因此本劇迅速地在同年12月成為[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]及[[華納兄弟電視公司|華納兄弟]]優先製作的喜劇影集。<ref name="Pilot Order">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/12/cbs-orders-single-mom-comedy-pilot-from-chuck-lorre-two-and-a-half-men-writers/|title=CBS Orders Single Mom Comedy Pilot From Chuck Lorre & 'Two And A Half Men' Writers|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2012-12-12|accessdate=2012-12-12|archive-date=2014-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140619153006/http://www.deadline.com/2012/12/cbs-orders-single-mom-comedy-pilot-from-chuck-lorre-two-and-a-half-men-writers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本劇於12月11日獲得CBS試播集預訂，由洛里和《[[好漢兩個半|好漢兩個半]]》班底執行製作{{link-en|艾迪·高洛達斯奇|Eddie Gorodetsky}}及編審潔瑪·貝克（{{lang|en|Gemma Baker}}）共同執筆，描述一名居住於加州[[納帕縣|納帕縣]]剛戒癮的母親，如何重振自己人生的故事。<ref name="Pilot Order"/>

2013年2月7日，宣布{{link-en|帕美拉·福瑞曼|Pamela Fryman}}將執導試播集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2013/02/pam-fryman-to-helm-second-pilot-larry-charles-mike-fresco-also-on-directing-duty-424745/|title=Pam Fryman To Helm Second Pilot; Larry Charles, Mike Fresco Also On Directing Duty|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2013-02-07|accessdate=2017-04-25|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025024035/https://deadline.com/2013/02/pam-fryman-to-helm-second-pilot-larry-charles-mike-fresco-also-on-directing-duty-424745/|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月8日，CBS宣布預訂本系列。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/chuck-lorres-cbs-pilot-mom-to-get-series-order-tomorrow/|title=Chuck Lorre's CBS Pilot 'Mom' To Get Series Order Tomorrow|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline.com|date=2013-05-08|accessdate=2013-05-08|archive-date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140806201043/http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/chuck-lorres-cbs-pilot-mom-to-get-series-order-tomorrow/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在本劇製作同時，洛里手上已有《好漢兩個半》、《[[生活大爆炸|生活大爆炸]]》與《[[邁克和茉莉|邁克和茉莉]]》3部影集，使得本劇成為洛里第4部同時製作播映的作品。隔週，CBS宣布本劇將於星期一晚上9點30分首播，緊接在《[[破產姐妹|破產姐妹]]》之後。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/05/15/cbs-announces-2013-2014-primetime-schedule-659502/20130515cbs01/|title=CBS Announces 2013-2014 Primetime Schedule|work=[[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]]|date=2013-05-15|accessdate=2013-05-15|archive-date=2013-09-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JPY7Su0F?url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/05/15/cbs-announces-2013-2014-primetime-schedule-659502/20130515cbs01/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在《{{link-en|大老爺們|We Are Men}}》被取消後，《破產姐妹》提前至晚間8點30分首播，在《邁克和茉莉》回歸以前，晚間9點則是安排《生活大爆炸》重播與本劇搭配。2013年10月18日，CBS宣布預訂第1季全季集數22集。<ref>{{cite press release|last=Bibel|first=Sara|title=CBS Gives Full Season Orders to 'The Crazy Ones', 'The Millers' & 'Mom'|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/10/18/cbs-gives-full-season-orders-to-the-crazy-ones-the-millers-mom/209992/|work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|date=2013-10-18|access-date=2016-02-04|archive-date=2013-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021042804/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/10/18/cbs-gives-full-season-orders-to-the-crazy-ones-the-millers-mom/209992/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

