7/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/mom-harry-hamlin-season-3-818285|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月23日，宣布《[[魔力麥克_XXL|魔力麥克 XXL]]》[[喬·曼根尼羅|喬·曼根尼羅]]將客串飾演匿名戒酒會性感的新進成員朱利安。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/article/2015/10/23/joe-manganiello-mom-guest-star/|title=Joe Manganiello to guest-star on Mom|publisher=娛樂周刊|author=Lynette Rice|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2017-04-25|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130184151/https://ew.com/article/2015/10/23/joe-manganiello-mom-guest-star/|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月28日，宣布《{{link-en|已婚 (電視節目)|Married (TV series)|已婚}}》[[茱蒂·葛瑞兒|茱蒂·葛瑞兒]]將客串飾演克莉絲蒂與邦妮嘗試幫助戒酒癮的米雪兒。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2015/10/28/mom-judy-greer-season-3-cast-cbs/|title=''Mom'' Enlists Judy Greer for 'Sloppy' November Sweeps Guest Stint|publisher=TVLine|author=Michael Ausiello|date=2015-10-28|accessdate=2017-04-25|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126094219/https://tvline.com/2015/10/28/mom-judy-greer-season-3-cast-cbs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月31日，宣布[[琳達·拉文|琳達·拉文]]將客串飾演格雷戈里的母親菲莉絲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2015/10/31/mom-linda-lavin-season-3-mother-in-law-cast/|title=''Mom'' Casts Linda Lavin as Violet's Future Mother-In-Law|publisher=TVLine|author=Michael Ausiello|date=2015-10-31|accessdate=2017-04-25|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126084754/https://tvline.com/2015/10/31/mom-linda-lavin-season-3-mother-in-law-cast/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

