==評價==
[[File:Allison_Janney_Oct_2014_(cropped).jpg|150px]]憑藉本劇榮獲2座[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]肯定}}]]
《極品老媽》獲得了普遍的好評，尤其是對於主演[[艾莉森·珍妮|艾莉森·珍妮]]與[[安娜·法瑞絲|安娜·法瑞絲]]的演技。於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得66%新鮮度、5.59/10分（35位評論家），評論家共識：「不可否認安娜·法瑞絲與艾莉森·珍妮確實激盪出喜劇火花，有時笑點太過粗俗，但《極品老媽》卻真誠地（有時充滿機智）點出成癮議題。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/mom/s01/|title=Mom: Season 1|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2016-02-04|archive-date=2017-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202171536/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/mom/s01/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第2季獲得100%新鮮度、8.5/10分（6位評論家）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/mom/s02/|title=Mom: Season 2|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2016-02-04|archive-date=2017-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127155634/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/mom/s02|dead-url=no}}</ref>第3季獲得100%新鮮度、8.33/10分（9位評論家）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/mom/s03/|title=Mom: Season 3|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2018-04-14|archive-date=2017-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203081626/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/mom/s03/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得65分（滿分100分；25位評論家），屬普遍的好評。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/mom|title=Mom - Season 1 Reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2015-01-04|archive-date=2020-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306002710/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/mom|dead-url=no}}</ref>第2季獲得81分（滿分100分；4位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/mom/season-2|title=Mom - Season 2 Reviews|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2015-01-04|archive-date=2020-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306013954/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/mom/season-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>第3季獲得82分（滿分100分；4位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/mom/season-3|title=Mom - Season 3 Reviews|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2017-04-27|archive-date=2020-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306013946/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/mom/season-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>

